{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_09_03",
  "title": "白石沙季 3話 今この時を全力で輝きます",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（なるほど。沙季は、ずっとそばで千紗のことを）\n（見てきたからな。思うことも多かったはずだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I see. Saki has been watching Chisa）\n（the whole time. She must have a lot of thoughts about it.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.2964975201,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 8.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "私にとって、千紗は大事な妹で、ライバルですから\n出来るなら、同じステージの上で――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For me‚ Chisa is an important younger sister‚ and a rival.\nIf possible‚ I'd like to be on the same stage --",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 17.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "並んで、競い合って、手を取り合って、一緒に輝きたい\nBIG4になった今だからこそ、そう強く思うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "standing side by side‚ competing‚ holding hands‚ and shining together.\nThat's what I feel so strongly now that I'm a BIG4 member.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……沙季の想いはきっちり受け取ったよ\n月ストとサニピの対戦が出来るように動いてみる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I've received your feelings properly‚ Saki.\nI'll see what I can do to make a match between Moon Tempest and Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 35.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "本当ですか！？\nあ、でも……他の仕事に影響が出るようであれば……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really!?\nAh‚ but… if it seems like it will affect other work…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 42.2666679382
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫、やりようはいくらでもある\n沙季は安心して、目の前の仕事に励んでくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's okay‚ there are plenty of ways to do it.\nJust relax‚ Saki‚ and focus on the work in front of you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 48.5666679382
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\n本当にありがとうございます。よろしくお願いしますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…\nThank you so much. I'm counting on you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.1000012715
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.3000012715
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――MV撮影当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――On the Day of the MV Shoot",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.1000012715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "うん、今日に向けてみんなしっかり準備を\nしてきたみたいだな。自信満々、って感じだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ everyone seems to have prepared well\nfor today. They seem full of confidence.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.9666687012
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます\n体調もバッチリですし、五人とも絶好調ですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you.\nWe're all in great shape‚ and all five of us are in top condition.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "私達全員、ライブバトルも含めたいろんな経験を\n経て、表現力がぐっと上がった気がするんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All of us have had various experiences‚ including live battles‚\nand I feel like our expressiveness has improved a lot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.7000020345
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "今の五人で撮影したMVがどうなるのか……\n凄く楽しみです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder how the MV with all five of us will turn out…\nI can't wait to see it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ここまで頼もしい言葉を聞けるとはな。俺も楽しみだよ\nそうだ。せっかくなら今伝えておこう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never thought I'd hear such reassuring words. I'm looking forward to it too.\nOh‚ right. Since we're here‚ I'll tell you now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "沙季に朗報があるんだ\n月ストとサニピの対戦が決まったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have some good news for Saki.\nThe match between Moon Tempest and Sunny Peace has been decided.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.4000020345
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "本当ですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.4000020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.4666687012
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。元々決まっていた\nサニピと共演予定の音楽番組があっただろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. There was a music show\nwith Sunny Peace that was originally planned‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "その中で、対戦出来ないか番組側に提案したらOKが\n出たんだ。ただし、エキシビジョンマッチだけどな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I suggested to the program that we have a match‚\nthey said OK. Well‚ it's just an exhibition match though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.1666625977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.5999979656
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "問題ありません。ランキングに変動がなくても\nお互いに本気も本気、真剣勝負になると思いますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's no problem. Even if it doesn’t affect the rankings‚\nI think it will be a serious competition where both side giving it their all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.0333292644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……今日は、本当に思い入れのある曲の撮影なので\nやる気満々だったんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu… Since we're shooting a song that's really special to me today‚\nso I was already full of motivation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.9333292644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.2999979656
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんのおかげで……\n一段と気合いを入れて臨めそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And thanks to {user}…\nI feel like I can take it on with even more enthusiasm.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.999995931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "この曲に込めた想いを、表情とポーズで表現……よし\nでは、こんな感じでどうでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Showing the feelings put into this song with my expressions and poses… Alright‚\nWell‚ how about something like this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.1666625977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "（千紗。いろいろ……本当にいろいろなことがあった）\n（けど、やっと千紗の隣に、胸を張って並べる気がする）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Chisa‚ so many things have happened… so many things.）\n（But‚ I finally feel like I can stand proudly next to Chisa.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.9666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "（千紗はいつも「お姉ちゃんがいてくれたから」）\n（って言ってくれるけど……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Chisa always says‚ \"It's because big sister was there.\"）\n（but…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.4900081381,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "（私も、千紗がそばにいてくれたから、照らしてくれた）\n（から、こうして走り続けてこれたんだよ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It's also because Chisa was by my side‚ and because she shone on me‚）\n（I've been able to keep running like this.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.100004069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_03-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "（千紗のおかげで、私は立ちあがることが出来た）\n（前よりも比べ物にならないくらい強くなれた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Thanks to Chisa‚ I was able to stand up.）\n（I've become stronger than I ever was before.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.2999949137,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
