      "text": "（静かで、それでいて凛とした決意のようなものを感じる）\n（今の沙季だからこそ出来る表情だな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I feel something like a quiet but dignified resolve.）\n（That's the kind of expression that only the current Saki can make.）",
